{
  "stem": "22047.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And oh my gosh, you know, to have a twin killed, the effect on the brother must have been really bad when he found out about it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was-- it was terrible for me and my people, because, like I said, a member of the family.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In the States, it turned out that-- that these two brothers would harassed the dickens out of us officers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You know, they-- they were right on the border of being insubordinate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And-- but they never were quite.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But they-- they-- they really gave us a hard time, these couple of sergeants.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were brothers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they were pretty feisty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But in combat, they were-- they were excellent soldiers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I felt a great loss and when-- when Lloyd was killed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And after-- after that episode, we moved back, as I mentioned earlier, moved back to an area.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that was before we got into-- to this position where I had taken this patrol out, and two of my people were killed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were in a place near Hagenow, which is in Alsace-Lorraine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Hagenow and Schweighausen were two of the cities that were in the-- near the Black Forest.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we did a lot of fighting in the forest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, I learned early on that if you're in a forest and you-- some artillery rounds are coming into that forest.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they're bursting in the trees above you, that you don't fall on the ground.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You stand behind a tree.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I taught my guys to do that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Don't ever hit the dirt when you hear an artillery round coming, because they whine and then they hit in the top of the trees.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And if you're lying on the ground, you're going to get hurt.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
